com.huawei.ipr.pof.manager.database

Class PMSwitchDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.huawei.ipr.pof.manager.database.PMSwitchDatabase

  • public class PMSwitchDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    SMSwitchDatabase is a part of SMDatabase, it stores data belonged to a switch.
    SMSwitchDatabase stores:
    • Ports
    • TableResource
    • Flow Tables
    • Flow Entries (stored in PMFlowTableDatabase)
    • Counters
    • GroupMods
    • MeterMods
    • LoggedMessages
    • SentMessage (for roll back)
    Author:
    Song Jian (jack.songjian@huawei.com), Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd.
